'''Homthor Deck''' was one of many aboard the [[Mon Calamari/Legends|Mon Calamari]] designed [[M-class|''M''-class]] [[Luxury liner/Legends|luxury liner]], the [[Kuari Princess/Legends|''Kuari Princess'']]. Passengers' starerooms were situated on Homthor Deck. Along with [[Wellad Deck]], the two were referred to as the "credicruise decks."<ref name="ACPOV">{{JournalCite|8|A Certain Point of View (short story)}}</ref>

